DTEND;TZID=Europe/Rome:20260608T120000
SUMMARY:[EDGECASE] Empty fragments between semicolons (Paolo Ricci, University of Bologna; ; Sara Moretti; Tommaso Villa, University of Trento)
LOCATION:Room D
DESCRIPTION:<p>Case 8: includes an empty author fragment between two semicolons. It should be ignored.</p>
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:debug-009-author-comma-empty-inst@example.test
DTSTAMP:20260520T100000Z
DTSTART;TZID=Europe/Rome:20260609T110000
DTEND;TZID=Europe/Rome:20260609T120000
SUMMARY:[EDGECASE] Author with trailing comma but no institution (Umberto Costa, ; Valeria Mancini, University of Padua)
LOCATION:Room E
DESCRIPTION:<p>Case 9: first author has an empty institution after comma. It should render as just the author name.</p>
